section.section:
Upon written request by the Child Support Enforcement Administration, any agency of this State, political subdivision of this State, employer, or labor union shall provide, if available, a person's:
Social Security account number;
date of birth;
last known residence or mailing address;
present or last known employer;
length of employment;
job classification;
name of person to be notified in case of emergency and the person's residence;
work hours;
amounts of wages or other assets; and
medical insurance provider.
